it.polimi.middlewaretechfordistsys.p2.http.HttpServer
public class HttpServer
extends akka.http.javadsl.server.AllDirectives
Akka main class, which is a http server that handles all the incoming requests. On the other hand, it exchanges messages with the computing actor through the local client actor.
